And no celebration is complete without making it special for our loved ones, isn’t it?! 💮 Bring home the festivities with @pantaloonsfashion and make the festive season a time to remember! 💝

The new flagship @acerindia Mall Exclusive Store just opened up in Phoenix Market City, Velacheri and we can’t believe just how super swanky it is! 

It’s got all of the best and newest of Acer’s products and trust us, the list of how good their features are gets long - be it the creative prowess of the Swift X series or the working traveler’s favourite, Swift 3. We also loved the absolutely gorgeous and sleek Spin series and the gamer’s obvious go-to option, Acer Nitro 5 with Ryzen and Intel processors. 

Gamers, pay attention! The store also has a dedicated gaming section with the technological wonder that the Predator Thronos is. Clearly, the store is not just a place to shop from, but an entire experience zone. Visit today for your share of experiential gaming!
